casebody.data:
Jeneir BRADSHER
v.
Shevene BRYANT and Sasha Sanders. No. 381P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 6, 2005. Lee D. Andrews, Greensboro, for Bradsher. Paul A. Daniels, Greensboro, for Shevene Bryant. G. Clark Herring, for Sanders.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 14th day of June 2005 by Plaintiff in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th day of October 2005."
